{"id":10822,"date":"2022-11-16T20:23:16","date_gmt":"2022-11-16T14:53:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/?p=10822"},"modified":"2023-01-06T19:28:18","modified_gmt":"2023-01-06T13:58:18","slug":"steps-you-should-not-dodge-off-while-hiring-a-team-of-dedicated-developers","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/steps-you-should-not-dodge-off-while-hiring-a-team-of-dedicated-developers.html","title":{"rendered":"Steps You Should Not Dodge-Off While Hiring A Team Of Dedicated Developers in 2023"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10824 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/Hire_Dedicated_Developers_Hiddenbrains.jpg\" alt=\"hire-dedicated-developers\" width=\"908\" height=\"441\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/Hire_Dedicated_Developers_Hiddenbrains.jpg 908w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/Hire_Dedicated_Developers_Hiddenbrains-300x146.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/Hire_Dedicated_Developers_Hiddenbrains-768x373.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 908px) 100vw, 908px\" \/><br \/>\nVirtual businesses have been steadily increasing over the past few years. This has been especially evident with companies that focus on online marketing. COVID -19 was a monumental conference for the virtual world, and there was no doubt that companies are taking advantage of the existing opportunities.<\/p>\n<p>Companies are now choosing to offer these services through their websites and apps, which makes it easier for people to find what they are looking for. This convenience is also a big draw for consumers, as they can buy and sell goods without going to a physical store.<\/p>\n<p>With the right app, you can attract new customers, deliver a great buying experience, and accelerate your business growth.<\/p>\n<p>When you need digital solutions like websites, mobile and web apps, enterprise solutions, and the like, you need people to build them. Digital solutions are becoming increasingly popular, so more people are looking for builders to create these types of things for them. This is a good thing because it means more people are available to build the solutions people need.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Why_there_is_a_need_to_Hire_Dedicated_Developers\"><\/span>Why there is a need to Hire Dedicated Developers?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Software developers, programmers, and platform specialists are in high demand as companies switch their businesses to automation and digital platforms. With so much change, the demand for these professionals is increasing.<\/p>\n<p>The requirement to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/hire-dedicated-developers.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hire dedicated developers<\/a> is growing exponentially due to the ever-growing need for software solutions. With the advent of the internet, more developers are needed to create innovative applications that meet customers&#8217; needs. This is because the internet has enabled people to connect in ways never before. There are now more opportunities for people to learn new things and develop their skills.<\/p>\n<p>Checking the app&#8217;s progress is essential to ensure the business gets the app it needs. You should do this regularly and make suggestions when necessary.<\/p>\n<p>As a business owner, you probably know there is no better way to build an efficient app than hiring a dedicated developer or Hire Web Developers for your project. A dedicated developer will not only make sure that your app is up to date and functioning correctly, but they will also be able to help you build it the way you want it. This can save you time and money in the long run.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_do_you_understand_by_the_dedicated_developer\"><\/span>What do you understand by the dedicated developer?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>A dedicated developer is hired for a specific amount of time by a business or a software development company to develop an application or website. Generally, dedicated developers are contracted for a set period, during which they are solely responsible for developing a specific project.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You get the best of both worlds when you hire a dedicated developer. You get someone who is dedicated to your project from start to finish, and you don&#8217;t have to worry about the developer&#8217;s other commitments. This model of hiring helps businesses complete their projects in time or fix software bugs, update apps, and so on.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A dedicated team is best if you&#8217;re looking for a developer to help you complete your project quickly and efficiently. They&#8217;ll get the job done quickly and to your satisfaction with the right tools and guidance.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now, if you&#8217;re like most businesses, you may wonder how to find the right developers. In fact, according to a recent study, finding the right developers can be one of the most challenging tasks a business can face. There are so many candidates, and it can be hard to decide which one to pick. To make things even more complicated, you don&#8217;t want to choose the wrong developer because your business could end up with a project that&#8217;s not up to par.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Things_to_consider_when_you_Hire_Dedicated_Developers\"><\/span>Things to consider when you Hire Dedicated Developers<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Before hiring a dedicated developer, you should consider various factors that will help you to build a strong and dedicated developer team. Consider your business needs and what type of developer is best suited for the job. You should also search for a developer with experience with the specific project you are working on. Hiring a developer who is not dedicated to your company will lead to frustration and wasted time.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here we have compiled a list of essentials that need to be taken care of while hiring dedicated developers:<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Assess_their_Background\"><\/span>Assess their Background<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The best way to choose a company and a developer is to do a little research, read more about the developer and the company, and check which products they have developed to date. After doing this, ask for the results they have achieved.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You want to see if the developer has any successful past projects that you can look into for inspiration. You want to ensure you are working with someone capable of completing your project on time and to the best of their ability. Compare the results to what you are looking for and make a decision. If the developer is reputable, they should be able to provide you with a list of their previous projects. These projects will give you a good idea of their skills and the quality of their work.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When you decide to Hire Mobile App Developers, you don&#8217;t want to end up with an overworked development team, unable to meet deadlines, or simply unprofessional. Look for companies with positive reviews and compare their rates to the others. It&#8217;s also a good idea to reserve charging slots as soon as possible. This will ensure that you have enough bandwidth for your app.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Interview_Developers\"><\/span>Interview Developers<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Developers are in high demand these days, but hiring an in-house developer is not always necessary. There are many outsourcing options out there that can save you time and money.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">They should always conduct interviews when hiring a developer, whether you are a small business or a large one. This way, you can be sure that the person you are hiring is qualified for the position and has the skills you need.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Communication Process<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Communication between developers and business owners is essential for the development process. Regular communication is vital so misunderstandings can be avoided and the development process can move forward smoothly.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When you are interacting with the team, it is important to figure out if there are any communication obstacles. To do this, you will need to ask the team members questions and observe their responses. If they do not seem to be bonding well with each other, then it might be a good idea to take some steps to rectify the situation. It results in an app solution that is perfect from every angle.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Scan their Reviews<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The companies often know the developers they work for. This is not always a good thing, as it gives the company too much power over the developer. Those who have worked with developers for a while know their strengths and weaknesses. Asking around for recommendations is a great way to get a feel for a developer&#8217;s work. Not just anyone, but those who had hired them are usually the best people to give an opinion.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Check out their website, read some of their reviews, and compare them to other companies. Asking for references is also a good idea. Choosing a company and developer that will be a good fit for your project is important.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"When_to_hire_Dedicated_resources_for_your_app_project\"><\/span><b>When to hire Dedicated resources for your app project?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Long-term_Projects\"><\/span><b><i>Long-term Projects<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Dedicated software development resources can be precious to enterprises when planning a project that will likely run longer than a few months. Companies can avoid potential delays and ensure a successful outcome by ensuring that the right people are working on the project from the start.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Unclear_Scope\"><\/span><b><i>Unclear Scope<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Businesses can save time and money by using dedicated resources for their project, as they can handle changing project requirements better. Businesses that do not clearly understand their development scope can be out of trouble if they decide to go with dedicated resources. With project requirements constantly changing, having a dedicated team on board will make adapting much easier.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Long-term_Support\"><\/span><b><i>Long-term Support<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Long-term support and maintenance for enterprise apps can be a burden for companies that need it. As they need to make constant changes in the software as per users&#8217; demands, a dedicated resource comes in handy here. With a dedicated resource, the enterprise can have quick and convenient access to support and updates for their app. This can save them time and money in the long run.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Agile_Methodology\"><\/span><b><i>Agile Methodology<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Agility is a trending technology enabling enterprises to get a solution built as per customers&#8217; requirements. By doing this, organizations can shorten the time it takes to deliver a product or service to their customers and maintain a competitive edge. Agility has revolutionized how products are delivered and can help you improve your speed to market, quality of delivery, and scalability.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And a dedicated resource is the best bet to serve this purpose!<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Business_Model_of_Hiring_Dedicated_Developers\"><\/span><b>Business Model of Hiring Dedicated Developers<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A pricing model can be categorized into two types: time-based and cost-based. Time-based pricing models involve charging a customer based on the amount of time they use the service, while cost-based pricing models involve setting a customer based on the actual resources used.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dedicated_Developers\"><\/span><b>Dedicated Developers<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With a cost-based pricing model, you charge customers based on the total work they submit. A dedicated business model allows you to control your team and keep yourself updated with the project status.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can also outsource your product development to dedicated developers hourly, weekly, and monthly. This will give you a quality product faster and at a lower cost.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Time_Material\"><\/span><b>Time &amp; Material<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the time &amp; material business model, numerous benefits can be realized. First and foremost, this model is more efficient because it allows businesses to save time and money. Additionally, this model will enable companies to focus on their most important tasks while leaving the less critical tasks to the workers.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Developers work on an hourly basis, and they usually follow time &amp; material business plans. This means they need to be aware of the time they are working and the amount of material they are taking in.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Fixed_Cost\"><\/span><b>Fixed Cost<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fixed costs are popular among businesses for a variety of reasons. They are comfortable dealing with, as well as giving attention to, time and money.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When you Hire Dedicated Developers with the fixed cost model, the client is given a set price for development, regardless of the features that are included in the application. The client is then responsible for covering any additional costs. The client prefers this model when developing an application that is known and when the client is well prepared with its internal features for the particular application.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Irresistible_benefits_of_Hiring_a_Dedicated_Developer\"><\/span><b>Irresistible benefits of Hiring a Dedicated Developer<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Overall_Responsibility\"><\/span><b><i>Overall Responsibility<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When you hire a dedicated developer team, they will take complete responsibility for the overall project. This means you won&#8217;t need to worry about any details, leaving more time to focus on your business.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Better_Outcome\"><\/span><b><i>Better Outcome<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Scheduling a team can be challenging, but it&#8217;s important to get it right. With this model, a PM will ensure that each team member has different work schedules and manage them accordingly. He\/She can define each team member&#8217;s schedule, work progress, and performance output.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Improved_Focus\"><\/span><b><i>Improved Focus<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A well-developed development team can efficiently perform complex tasks without the need for you to get involved. You can delegate tasks to them and let them take care of the development process while you focus on other tasks.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cost-Effective\"><\/span><b><i>Cost-Effective<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The dedicated developer model is also cost-effective as the client doesn&#8217;t have to pay high wages for an experienced freelancer. This model allows businesses to acquire the necessary skillset without incurring high costs.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_Much_does_it_Cost_to_Hire_Dedicated_Developers_with_Hidden_Brains\"><\/span><b>How Much does it Cost to Hire Dedicated Developers with Gozoom Technologies?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cost is an ever-green discussion topic, and there is no point in avoiding it. At Gozoom Technologies- an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Offshore Software Development Company<\/a>, we very well comprehend business needs; hence we offer flexibility in pricing and scalability when you hire dedicated developers